CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 10, 1957, pg. 14 reads: "Visiting Pittsburgh to take part in ABA tournament were some gorgeous gals and handsome men. Here, left to right, are...Mrs. Doris Brooks, Brooklyn, N.Y...."Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 10, 1957, pg. 14 reads: "Clyde Woolridge...ranks with best"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Doris Brooks wearing paisley dress, and Clyde Woolridge, posed in Fort Pitt Hotel for 24th annual American Bridge Association tournament
